  "quest.6120A9478D66C2F9.quest_desc": {
    "original": "With the \u0026aStraw\u0026r that you've made, you are finally able to make a basic version of the most important tool on your journey: \u00263The Crude Brush\u0026r.\n\nWith a gentle hand and a stroke of the \u00263Brush\u0026r, you'll be able to find the minerals hidden inside the broken stones.\n\nYou should return to the \u0026dEcho of Guidance\u0026r to show him your progress.\n\n\u0026eNote\u0026r: You can use /spawn to return to the lobby.",
    "translation": "透過你剛剛製造出來的\u0026a稻梗\u0026r，你終於能夠做出這趟旅程中最重要的工具......的基本版：\u00263粗製刷子\u0026r。\n\n使用\u00263刷子\u0026r輕輕幾划，你就能夠找到藏於破碎石頭中的細小礦物。\n\n是時候返回\u0026d指引嚮導之回聲\u0026r處，向他報告你的進展了。\n\n\u0026e備註\u0026r：你可以使用「/spawn」指令回到大廳。",
    "context": "chapters/thebackrooms.snbt / quest 6120A9478D66C2F9",
    "meta": {
      "line_split_policy": "lf",
      "snbt_value_shape": "list_of_string"
    }
  },
