  "quest.6D5A9E9E8B0D8AC2.quest_desc": {
    "original": "With the materials you've gathered, you should be able to craft the \u00263Chronon Generator\u0026r like the \u0026dEcho\u0026r wanted!\n\nIt's time to submit the \u0026aChronon Generator\u0026r and return to the \u0026dEcho of Guidance\u0026r. Doing this will award all players on your team a \u0026aCell\u0026r and a \u00262Generator\u0026r.\n\n\u0026eNote\u0026f: You must submit the \u0026aChronon Generator\u0026r to complete this quest and update the \u0026dEcho of Guidance\u0026r. ",
    "translation": "使用你剛剛採集到的資源，你就可以合成出\u0026d回聲\u0026r想要的\u00263時空粒子產生器\u0026r了！\n\n是時候交出\u0026a時間粒子產生器\u0026r並返回\u0026d指引嚮導之回聲\u0026r處了。完成這項任務會給予你隊伍中的所有玩家各一台\u0026a單元\u0026r和一台\u0026r產生器\u0026r。\n\n\u0026e備註\u0026f：你會需要提交這台\u0026a時空粒子產生器\u0026r才能完成這項任務並取得\u0026d指引嚮導之回聲\u0026r的下一步指示。",
    "context": "chapters/thebackrooms.snbt / quest 6D5A9E9E8B0D8AC2",
    "meta": {
      "line_split_policy": "lf",
      "snbt_value_shape": "list_of_string"
    }
  },
